tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/just/wp-call/2021-2022/call-fiche_just-2022-jtra_en.pdf \" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/just/agr-contr/general-mga_just_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Mono/Multi-beneficiary Model Grant Agreement</a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/sites/default/files/c_2021_2699_f1_commission_implementing_decision_en_v3_p1_1177590.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Justice 2021-22 Work Programme</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=uriserv%3AOJ.L_.2021.156.01.0021.01.ENG&amp;toc=OJ%3AL%3A2021%3A156%3ATOC\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Regulation establishing the Justice Programme</span></a></p>", "supportInfo": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">For help related to this <b>call</b>, please contact: </span><a href=\"mailto:ec-justice-calls@ec.europa.eu\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#xA;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#xA;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">ec-justice-calls@ec.europa.eu</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><a href=\"https://ec.