></span></p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service, please click on the submission-button next to the <strong>type of action</strong> and the <strong>type of model grant agreement</strong> that corresponds to your proposal. You will then be asked to confirm your choice, as it cannot be changed in the submission system. Upon confirmation, you will be linked to the correct entry point.</p>\r\n<p>To access existing draft proposals for this topic, please login to the Funding &amp; Tenders Portal and select the My Proposals page of the My Area section.</p>", "links": [], "additionalDossiers": [], "infoPackDossiers": [], "callDetailsJSONItem": {"latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Jul 12, 2022 8:46:07 AM", "lastChangeDate": "Jul 12, 2022 8:46:07 AM", "content": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Call update flash info &ndash; call results</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Call for proposals: JUST-2022-JTRA </strong>Call for proposals for action grants to support transnational projects on judicial training  covering civil law, criminal law or fundamental rights</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Types of action</strong>: JUSTICE Project Grants</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Opening date</strong>: 15 December 2021</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Deadline</strong>: 22 March 2022 17:00:00</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Call's budget</strong>: 5 000 000 EUR</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Number of proposals submitted</strong>: 26</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Number of eligible proposals</strong>: 24</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Summary of the results</strong>:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Award of a grant to 11 proposals for the amount of EUR 4.901.380,35 (out of the total budget of EUR 5 000 000 foreseen for this call);</li>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 proposals were placed on the reserve list for the amount of EUR 849.514,24;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rejection of 11 proposals due to insufficient relevance and/or quality;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rejection of 2 ineligible proposals.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The results of the evaluation were communicated to the applicants through individual  letters on the Funding &amp; tender opportunities Portal on 8 July 2022</p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Jul 8, 2022 4:58:12 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Jul 8, 2022 4:58:12 PM", "content": "<p>The results of the evaluation&nbsp;are now available for: JUST-2022-JTRA.</p>"}, {"approvalDate": "Dec 15, 2021 12:02:24 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Dec 15, 2021 12:02:24 PM", "content": "The submission session is now available for: JUST-2022-JTRA(JUST-PJG)"}], "hasForthcomingTopics": false, "hasOpenTopics": false, "allClosedTopics": true}}}